{
  "stem": "18865.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandmother was Amilia, and she was born in-- she comes from-- from [NON-ENGLISH] really, which is just a-- just outside of Krefeld.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She lost her husband very early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and she had her own place with this aunt who conducted the Seder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They lived together, but then my aunt went to the United States, and my grandmother moved in with us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose the first thing that-- first time I [? met ?] notices when I have to leave school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1936, the-- I have wrote it all down, but 1937, yeah, 1937.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when I realized that life changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what to do next.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could not have maids anymore in the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a very large, three-story house and a living basement where my father had his office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a lot of work, but we were not allowed to have anymore Aryan maids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I-- when I left school, I actually worked, did a lot of housework, helped my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there is no comparison to what happened then in-- in '30-- in-- in '38 in the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was-- that was the final blow, and that's when I realized I must leave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I must get out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I must see that my family gets out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we heard in the morning of November 8, we-- no, wait.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the synagogues burned on-- on the night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the morning of the 9th of-- of November, the bell rang about 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I ran downstairs so early, and I opened the door, and it was my uncle, my father's brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, what are you doing here so early?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's going on?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
